=== Lmɣrib ===

* '''Tutlayt taclḥit''' nɣ tasusit tga tutlayt tamaziɣt akkʷ imqqurn ɣ wuṭṭun n imsawaln. tg tmazirt-nns ger adrar n drn, Asif n Sus, Asif n Dra d waṭlas imẓẓiyn. llan imsawaln sis ɣ tmdinin mqqurnin ula nttnti zun d [[Tigmmi Tumlilt|tigmmi tumlilt]], d [[Rrbaṭ|rrbaḍ]] d [[sla]]. Tga taclḥiyt yat zɣ tawja n tutlayin n waṭlas tama n tmaziɣt n waṭlas anammas.
* '''Tutlayt tamaziɣt n tuẓẓumt'''

